# Prewriting: is where we gathering information regarding to the topic.
# My topic for this writing process assignment: Bauer stereophonic-to-binaural DSP
# The information regarding to the BS2B can be found on the following link:
# Link: http://bs2b.sourceforge.net/

# FYI: BS2B is a advanced digital signal processing tool that can transform the typical stereophonic signals to 
# binaural signal to better retrive the actual sound of the digtal music files (enchance your listening experience).

Prewriting Layout for this assignment:

I. Introduction of the BS2B processing and why we need it.

II. How does the BS2B works and how can it enhance our listening experience, and comparision with stereo processing.

III. How BS2B works in reality.

IV. Conclusion.
